FBIS4-40279 "drsov116_a_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Nguyen Manh Cam Comments on Korea Nguyen Manh Cam Comments on Korea LD1506195494 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1926 GMT 15 Jun 94 LD1506195494 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent Andrey Kirillov] [Excerpt] Moscow June 15 TASS -- [passage omitted] Commenting on the situation on the Korean Peninsula, following North Korea's decision to withdraw from the IAEA, [Vietnamese Foreign Minister] Nguyen Manh Cam told ITAR-TASS after his talks with [Russian Foreign Minister] Kozyrev that there is still hope that the conflict can be settled through negotiations. He called for "finding such a solution which would respect the sovereignty and independence of all countries."
